00:51:01,199 --> 00:51:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa stvorite li.

1357
00:51:03,199 --> 00:51:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zar si za mene to stvorio.

1358
00:51:04,199 --> 00:51:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1359
00:51:05,199 --> 00:51:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] I baš tu jednu malu ne skrivenu.

1360
00:51:07,199 --> 00:51:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako sam naletio baš na me.

1361
00:51:08,199 --> 00:51:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sta mi svjesno da je život prijateljom čudesa.

1362
00:51:13,199 --> 00:51:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] I taj Isus dolazi da otvori tvoje prostore.

1363
00:51:16,199 --> 00:51:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže.

1364
00:51:17,199 --> 00:51:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne boj se grijeha.

1365
00:51:18,199 --> 00:51:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne boj se pata.

1366
00:51:19,199 --> 00:51:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam da otvorio.

1367
00:51:20,199 --> 00:51:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi živi čovječ.

1368
00:51:21,199 --> 00:51:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi čini dobro.

1369
00:51:23,199 --> 00:51:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Si slušao šta je u četvrtak pričao Ivač?

1370
00:51:25,199 --> 00:51:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čijesam.

1371
00:51:26,199 --> 00:51:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa idi ti tako drugima reci.

1372
00:51:27,199 --> 00:51:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi reci svojima doma.

1373
00:51:29,199 --> 00:51:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi reci djeci kojima predaješ.

1374
00:51:31,199 --> 00:51:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kojima si možda u vrtiću u školu.

1375
00:51:33,199 --> 00:51:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi reci starci bak su u staraškom domu.

1376
00:51:35,199 --> 00:51:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Idi reci bolestnicima.

1377
00:51:36,199 --> 00:51:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] Reci im radosno vijez.

1378
00:51:37,199 --> 00:51:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da su slobodni.

1379
00:51:39,199 --> 00:51:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] Neka vjeruju dobro.

1380
00:51:41,199 --> 00:51:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] U zdravlje.

1381
00:51:42,199 --> 00:51:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] U zdravlje jače od bolesti.

1382
00:51:44,199 --> 00:51:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] Život jače od smrti.

1383
00:51:45,199 --> 00:51:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] Reci im.

1384
00:51:46,199 --> 00:51:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što postoje onaj.

1385
00:51:48,199 --> 00:51:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dok ne bih gledati u liječnike, u sebe, u svoju bolesti, u ljude.

1386
00:51:52,199 --> 00:51:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dote ste biti zločesti.

1387
00:51:54,199 --> 00:51:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čiji pogledaš samo malo više iznad ljudi.

1388
00:51:56,199 --> 00:51:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] O stvoritelj.

1389
00:51:57,199 --> 00:51:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da cvačaš.

1390
00:51:58,199 --> 00:52:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] O tebe dolazi sve ko kišica.

1391
00:52:00,199 --> 00:52:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] I gledajte kako ste svi ko jaganci.

1392
00:52:02,199 --> 00:52:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem pet minuta morate šutiti.

1393
00:52:04,199 --> 00:52:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vas, koliko, pet stotina, šest stotina.

1394
00:52:06,199 --> 00:52:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Svi šutite.

1395
00:52:07,199 --> 00:52:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] I pitao mi, kaže Ivanče, kako ti to uspiješ?

1396
00:52:10,199 --> 00:52:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mi imamo u školi, kaže 30 džaka pa svi brbljaju.

1397
00:52:13,199 --> 00:52:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] A ti šest to njih i svi ti ti še.

1398
00:52:17,199 --> 00:52:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ne bih prijatelje dragi.

1399
00:52:20,199 --> 00:52:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čude sad su mi dogat ruke.

1400
00:52:24,199 --> 00:52:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo tu drugu točku absolvirati.

1401
00:52:27,199 --> 00:52:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] A to znači, nama je poslan netko.

1402
00:52:30,199 --> 00:52:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nebo nije nepoznato.

1403
00:52:31,199 --> 00:52:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] Smrt nije nepoznata.

1404
00:52:33,199 --> 00:52:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Grih nije nepoznata.

1405
00:52:35,199 --> 00:52:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Milosrđe, oproštenje nije nepoznato.

1406
00:52:38,199 --> 00:52:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] Milosrđe Bože nije nepoznato.

1407
00:52:41,199 --> 00:52:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je samo poznato.

1408
00:52:42,199 --> 00:52:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je Isus iz Nazareta.

1409
00:52:44,199 --> 00:52:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] On je došao.

1410
00:52:46,199 --> 00:52:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] Križavine na našim crkvama pokazuju jasno.

1411
00:52:48,199 --> 00:52:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] Križavine na našim, oko vrata, na našim lančićima pokazuju.

1412
00:52:52,199 --> 00:52:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] Gled to je On, oslobađa me.

1413
00:52:54,199 --> 00:52:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se križam, gled to On mene oslobađa.

1414
00:52:56,199 --> 00:53:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ma gdje god sam, dođete k mene umorni opeređeni.

1415
00:53:00,199 --> 00:53:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je naroda.

1416
00:53:03,199 --> 00:53:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dajte im vijesti.

1417
00:53:05,199 --> 00:53:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Napravi čudo da se najedeš čovječe.

1418
00:53:07,199 --> 00:53:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sve će učiniti za tebe.

1419
00:53:09,199 --> 00:53:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je ta druga istina.

1420
00:53:11,199 --> 00:53:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, radost i vijesti.

1421
00:53:13,199 --> 00:53:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] Joj Isuse, pa ti si moj prijatelj?

1422
00:53:15,199 --> 00:53:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

1423
00:53:17,199 --> 00:53:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] A što vi radite?

1424
00:53:18,199 --> 00:53:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vi dođete u crkvu, podam sve te vode,

1425
00:53:20,199 --> 00:53:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa se poškujete po malo nakon cupreneta, jel?

1426
00:53:23,199 --> 00:53:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa na brže, pred kip srca Islava.

1427
00:53:25,199 --> 00:53:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže, ja nisam kipak.

1428
00:53:30,199 --> 00:53:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] I opet, ja nisam kipak.

1429
00:53:34,199 --> 00:53:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Groz.

1430
00:53:36,199 --> 00:53:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Umeđa se da se samo sjetiš.

1431
00:53:38,199 --> 00:53:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ta kip nije nikakav Isus.

1432
00:53:40,199 --> 00:53:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno.

1433
00:53:41,199 --> 00:53:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] No, ta kip te podsjeća.

1434
00:53:43,199 --> 00:53:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je kao pisana riječ koja te podsjeća.

1435
00:53:45,199 --> 00:53:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je ljubav, Isus je ljubav.

1436
00:53:47,199 --> 00:53:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubi te, strašno.

1437
00:53:48,199 --> 00:53:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali živi Isus, ne ta kip.

1438
00:53:50,199 --> 00:53:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] A mi je da još taj kip pomilujem,

1439
00:53:52,199 --> 00:53:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda ponesem mnogo praha kuna.

1440
00:53:54,199 --> 00:53:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam mnogo praha kući.

1441
00:53:56,199 --> 00:53:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] I postajem u pogadnjem.

1442
00:53:58,199 --> 00:54:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kip je kateheza.

1443
00:54:03,199 --> 00:54:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kip je propoved.

1444
00:54:04,199 --> 00:54:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kip samo to obavještava, pa se ne zaboravi.

1445
00:54:07,199 --> 00:54:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] On je taj.

1446
00:54:08,199 --> 00:54:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo opet pet minuta.

1447
00:54:12,199 --> 00:54:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ubit ovo drugo.

1448
00:54:17,199 --> 00:54:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] Slobodu.

1449
00:54:18,199 --> 00:54:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorio mi vrata.

1450
00:54:20,199 --> 00:54:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedan greh me ne može spriječiti.

1451
00:54:22,199 --> 00:54:22,199
[UNKNOWN] Ne.

1452
00:54:22,199 --> 00:54:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedan čovjek.

1453
00:54:23,199 --> 00:54:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1454
00:54:24,199 --> 00:54:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Moje nebo.

1455
00:54:25,199 --> 00:54:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Moja budućnost.

1456
00:54:26,199 --> 00:54:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću biti zdrav.

1457
00:54:27,199 --> 00:54:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to hoću.

1458
00:54:28,199 --> 00:54:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to hoću.

1459
00:54:29,199 --> 00:54:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] I opet tu viziju.

1460
00:54:30,199 --> 00:54:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ej.

1461
00:54:31,199 --> 00:54:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prva vizija je bila stvoritelja temelj svega.

1462
00:54:35,199 --> 00:54:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] A druga vizija.

1463
00:54:36,199 --> 00:54:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] I stvoritelj je najvažniji.

1464
00:54:38,199 --> 00:54:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bez toga nema niš drugo.

1465
00:54:39,199 --> 00:54:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] A druga vizija.

1466
00:54:40,199 --> 00:54:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jopom čak posao svoga sina.

1467
00:54:42,199 --> 00:54:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da me oslobodi.

1468
00:54:43,199 --> 00:54:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ko mi šta može.

1469
00:54:45,199 --> 00:54:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] I taj sin je u meni.

1470
00:54:47,199 --> 00:54:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] Hm?

1471
00:54:48,199 --> 00:54:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] Što opet zatorit oči pa odspavati.

1472
00:54:49,199 --> 00:54:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Još pet mi je.

1473
00:54:50,199 --> 00:55:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je druga zadača koju ćete dakle do uskrsa.

1474
00:55:01,199 --> 00:55:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolvirati.

1475
00:55:02,199 --> 00:55:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem.

1476
00:55:03,199 --> 00:55:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer radi se o vama.

1477
00:55:04,199 --> 00:55:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ćete biti sretni.

1478
00:55:06,199 --> 00:55:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je najljepše onaj osiviti.

1479
00:55:09,199 --> 00:55:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam na sigurnom tru.

1480
00:55:11,199 --> 00:55:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je moj projekt.

1481
00:55:12,199 --> 00:55:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam moram samo to u sebe upiti.

1482
00:55:14,199 --> 00:55:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mene si drugi negativni, zločesti, bolesni mehanizmi vode i ubijaju.

1483
00:55:19,199 --> 00:55:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću da me ovaj mehanizam ljubavi.

1484
00:55:23,199 --> 00:55:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Treća još točka dakle o evangelizaciji u toj kerigmi.

1485
00:55:27,199 --> 00:55:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] Treća točka.

1486
00:55:28,199 --> 00:55:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što znači nova evangelizacija ili kerigma.

1487
00:55:31,199 --> 00:55:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ili evangelizacija.

1488
00:55:32,199 --> 00:55:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] To znači posijati.

1489
00:55:35,199 --> 00:55:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] biljčicu.

1490
00:55:37,199 --> 00:55:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Posijati biljčicu.

1491
00:55:39,199 --> 00:55:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki od vas poput žira, rekao sam sto puta.

1492
00:55:44,199 --> 00:55:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] U žiru.

1493
00:55:46,199 --> 00:55:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki normalan čovjek zna da je hrast.

1494
00:55:50,199 --> 00:55:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] U žiru je hrast.

1495
00:55:52,199 --> 00:55:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] I tko to ne vidi, taj patnik.

1496
00:55:56,199 --> 00:55:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] I taj nije razuman.

1497
00:55:58,199 --> 00:56:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] I taj ljadan čovjek.

1498
00:56:01,199 --> 00:56:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] U svakom žiru je hrast.

1499
00:56:04,199 --> 00:56:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] I radi se samo da li ću žir staviti u čep.

1500
00:56:09,199 --> 00:56:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Tad sam ljadan i bolestan.

1501
00:56:13,199 --> 00:56:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] I mrtavan.

1502
00:56:14,199 --> 00:56:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ću žir rastiti.

1503
00:56:16,199 --> 00:56:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ja posijem, tada mu rastem.

1504
00:56:19,199 --> 00:56:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] I od njega nastaje hrast.

1505
00:56:21,199 --> 00:56:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] taj hrast.

1506
00:56:22,199 --> 00:56:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je taj hrast?

1507
00:56:24,199 --> 00:56:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Taj hrast unutra u žiru?

1508
00:56:25,199 --> 00:56:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite.

1509
00:56:26,199 --> 00:56:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je taj projekt.

1510
00:56:28,199 --> 00:56:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] O što ja vama dajem, to su žirevi.

1511
00:56:30,199 --> 00:56:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali iz toga će propupati veličanstvena vaša dijela i sposobnost i inteligencija.

1512
00:56:37,199 --> 00:56:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet ćete.

1513
00:56:38,199 --> 00:56:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sposobnost, zdravlja, duha.

1514
00:56:40,199 --> 00:56:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sloboda.

1515
00:56:42,199 --> 00:56:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, treća točka je ono što trebamo znati.

1516
00:56:45,199 --> 00:56:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] A to je da je Bog poslao treću božansku osobu, duha svetoga.

1517
00:56:51,199 --> 00:56:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jedno je stvoritelj svijeta, otac, koji je od koga je sve, koji je temelj svega.

1518
00:56:56,199 --> 00:57:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo je sin, riječ njegova koja došla i otvorila nam vrata širom slobode od grijega i zla i paka.

1519
00:57:03,199 --> 00:57:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] Treća je poslan duh sveti.

1520
00:57:05,199 --> 00:57:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1521
00:57:06,199 --> 00:57:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da učini da mi možemo činiti ono što čini Isuse.

1522
00:57:10,199 --> 00:57:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi svojom ljudskom dušom ne možemo činiti ono što čini stvoritelj.

1523
00:57:15,199 --> 00:57:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što čini Isus koji je sin Bože.

1524
00:57:18,199 --> 00:57:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] I zato duh sveti dolaze, dakle, ja imam novog duha, novu dušu.

1525
00:57:23,199 --> 00:57:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] I dok moja duhovna duša mora biti zdrava, da bih ja bio inteligentan, sposoban, da bih ja mogao kao čovjek biti vrhunski, znanstvenik, umjetnik, radnik, seljak i tako dalje.

1526
00:57:36,199 --> 00:57:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dotovo je duh sveti dolaze da bi ja u smislu Božem rastao sa Božem narodom.

1527
00:57:40,199 --> 00:57:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer imam dvije narodi, ljudsku i božansku.

1528
00:57:43,199 --> 00:57:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] Po krštenju sam primio božansku.

1529
00:57:45,199 --> 00:57:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] I taj duh sveti u mene ustvaruje tu božansku.

1530
00:57:48,199 --> 00:58:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mi krivo činimo, kad hoćemo da nam duh sveti dade da imamo kruha, da imamo malo mlijeka, da pošalje nekog anđela pa da ti kupi crne kave, pa malo šećera ti fali.

1531
00:58:01,199 --> 00:58:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Duh sveti ne radi ništa drugo u nama.

1532
00:58:04,199 --> 00:58:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nego ono nadnaravno božansko u nama razvija da budemo kao Bog.

1533
00:58:09,199 --> 00:58:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ja kao čovjek Bog, nego duh sveti mene čini Bogom.

1534
00:58:16,199 --> 00:58:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što je utjelovio Isusa da umario, Marije Isus primio psihofizičku razivu.

1535
00:58:23,199 --> 00:58:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek postao je, a duh sveti mu da u tom čovjeku Isusu bude božanska velika sila.

1536
00:58:31,199 --> 00:58:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mogo čini čudesa.

1537
00:58:32,199 --> 00:58:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] I ti to možeš.

1538
00:58:34,199 --> 00:58:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si primio duha svijeta.

1539
00:58:36,199 --> 00:58:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Duh sveti je poslan u srca svih vjernika.

1540
00:58:39,199 --> 00:58:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] I on stanoja u našem tijelu kao hrano.

1541
00:58:42,199 --> 00:58:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je treća velika istina.

1542
00:58:44,199 --> 00:58:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] I kad si toga svijeta onda znaš, ti si žir.

1543
00:58:48,199 --> 00:58:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čovječe, ti si žir.

1544
00:58:50,199 --> 00:58:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Duh sveti je žir.

1545
